上贊助中天👉https://bit.ly/ctidonate (綠界金流/可用信用卡、ATM)\n💵直接贊助中天👉彰化銀行台北分行:009-5012帳號:50128688988600戶名:中天電視股份有限公司 \n🏧ATM：CHANG HWA COMMERCIAL BANK TAIPEI BRANCH(CCBCTWTP501) \n🏦A/C NO:50128688988600 A/C NAME:CTI TELEVISION INCORPORATION\n\n⚠️未經著作權人事先書面同意，勿將內容用於商業性質之分享、連結。 \n⚠️如有任何營業使用，必須事先取得書面同意。\n\n【中天聊天室規範】歡迎留言互動，請尊重各自立場、理性發言，請遵守本聊天室規範。 違規者一經發現，將遭刪言或封鎖。\n🚫禁止使用不雅、挑釁、謾罵、歧視、仇恨等言詞\n🚫禁止任何形式洗版 🚫禁止散布不實訊息 \n🚫禁止發表危害公共安全等涉及犯罪言論 \n🚫禁止傳送鼓勵博弈訊息\n🚫禁止色情服務訊息\n🚫禁止騷擾管理員與其他使用者\n📣管理員有權隨時修正規定 \n\nYouTube音樂庫 無版權配樂 免費背景音樂下載: https://goo.gl/Z6TsBI 歌名: Sunspots 作者: Jeremy Blake 類型: Dance \u0026 Electronic 氣氛: Happy Music YouTube音樂庫 台灣香港 - Follow Us YouTube: https://goo.gl/Z6TsBI Facebook: https://goo.gl/ikoMdk Google+: https://goo.gl/90orLC Instagram: https://goo.gl/lLAoUo","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":0,"length":4,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CCMQ3NcEGEkiEwj4rNDCubuGAxUM0D8EHeo8EGE=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/hashtag/%E8%B3%B4%E6%B8%85%E5%BE%B7","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_BROWSE","rootVe":6827,"apiUrl":"/youtubei/v1/browse"}},"browseEndpoint":{"browseId":"FEhashtag","params":"6gUNCgnos7TmuIXlvrcYAQ%3D%3D"}}},"loggingDirectives":{"trackingParams":"CCMQ3NcEGEkiEwj4rNDCubuGAxUM0D8EHeo8EGE=","enableDisplayloggerExperiment":true}},{"startIndex":4,"length":4,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CCIQ3NcEGEoiEwj4rNDCubuGAxUM0D8EHeo8EGE=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/hashtag/520","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_BROWSE","rootVe":6827,"apiUrl":"/youtubei/v1/browse"}},"browseEndpoint":{"browseId":"FEhashtag","params":"6gUHCgM1MjAYAQ%3D%3D"}}},"loggingDirectives":{"trackingParams":"CCIQ3NcEGEoiEwj4rNDCubuGAxUM0D8EHeo8EGE=","enableDisplayloggerExperiment":true}},{"startIndex":8,"length":7,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CCEQ3NcEGEsiEwj4rNDCubuGAxUM0D8EHeo8EGE=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/hashtag/%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%B0%B1%E8%81%B7%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_BROWSE","ro